737
01:24:33,047 --> 01:24:34,116
Bicu u redu.

738
01:24:39,647 --> 01:24:40,921
Srecno.

739
01:26:19,247 --> 01:26:20,282
Jesi li dobro?

740
01:26:20,687 --> 01:26:23,759
Da. A ti?

741
01:26:28,407 --> 01:26:32,366
